ll executed. The core idea was great, it was easy to use, it was fun and the main goal of adopting dogs from the SPCA animal shelters exceeded expectation.\r\n<h3>Recognition</h3>\r\nThis site has won numerous awards including the Grand Axis, Gold Cannes, Spikes, Caples and many others. It was also featured on Campbell Live when it first launched.', 'BK Brand Site', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '454-revision-3', '', '', '2013-01-16 20:14:51', '2013-01-16 08:14:51', '', 454, 'http://localhost/techblog/articles/454-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
