ry instead of the database. The other thing we did was archive matches more than 5 days old so that when we were doing a database look up the table wasn''t millions of rows long. All of these things combined with a queuing system allowed the server to tick over quite nicely despite the huge volume of traffic.\r\n<h3>Results</h3>\r\nThis project was both simple and well executed. The core idea was great, it was easy to use, it was fun and the main goal of adopting dogs from the SPCA animal shelters exceeded expectation.\r\n<h3>Recognition</h3>\r\nThis site has won numerous awards including the Grand Axis, Gold Cannes, Spikes, Caples and many others. It was also featured on Campbell Live when it first launched.', 'V Blue Facebook Tab', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '470-revision-6', '', '', '2013-01-16 20:59:00', '2013-01-16 08:59:00', '', 470, 'http://localhost/techblog/articles/470-revision-6/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
